data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED - BRING US AN OFFER! LISTED AT 80K BELOW RECENT APPRAISAL! Dreaming about that waterfront life? Look no further…welcome to Saint Johns River Acres community! This AMAZING waterfront home is beautifully situated on a DEEP WATER CANAL barely 100 yards from the opening to the St. Johns River. PRICED 40K BELOW RECENT APPRAISAL!! Bring any sized boat and pull right up to the dock giving you the most amazing piece of river front property you will find with so much versatility, features, and best of all….tranquility. This 1.5 Acre waterfront lot features 100 feet of direct canal frontage, full boat dock with a floating portion of the dock, your own PRIVATE CONCRETE BOAT RAMP, even the most amazing custom built treehouse complete with power and A/C!! This is absolutely one of the most unique properties you will find with so much to offer. The main house sits quietly near the rear of the property surrounded by soaring mature oak trees and giving you the most majestic tree-lined canopy above. The house has just been fitted with NEW ROOF just a year ago, NEW HVAC SYSTEM, NEW WELL AND BRAND NEW SEPTIC BEING INSTALLED CURRENTLY. As you walk up the stairs to the front door, you’ll find all living space on the 2nd floor, including a large living room, kitchen, 3 generously sized bedrooms, and a full bathroom. The living room and kitchen look out into the rear of the home giving you the most spectacular views of the water and bringing in tons of natural light. Enjoy the views, the tranquility, and the gorgeous Florida weather while sitting on the large screened in patio overlooking the backyard and the canal. On the bottom floor you’ll find an enormous enclosed garage space with workshop and tons of room and options for expanding. This space could easily be converted to more living space allowing for this home to nearly double in size. THIS IS ONE OF VERY FEW RIVER FRONT PROPERTIES THAT DID NOT FLOOD DURING THE STORMS. HIGH AND DRY!! Situated 22 feet in the air and right at the center of the property you will find a fully livable and enclosed CUSTOM BUILT TREEHOUSE with power, A/C, and picturesque views of this beautiful property. The home is located in a private river front community, nestled back beyond conservation, and although it offers privacy and rural type seclusion, it is still only 10 minutes from major shopping, restaurants, and nearby grocery stores. River life is the best life, and you will love being just minutes down the river from Blue Springs National Park, Swamp House River Front Grill, Lake George, Silver Glenn, and many other amazing St Johns River spots. Bring the boat, bring all the motorized toys, bring the RV, you can have it all….right here on Detroit Terrace.
